Vendors are encouraged to include additional content beyond MUST-HAVE criteria:

| ID | Area | What to Include |
|---|---|---|
| **N-1** | **Vendor-Proposed Differentiators** | Capabilities not covered in MUST-HAVE criteria that the vendor believes are relevant. |
| **N-2** | **Implementation Plan** | Proposed phased approach, timeline, milestones, resource model. |
| **N-3** | **Licensing Model Overview** | Pricing model structure (not dollar amounts) — consumption, seat-based, reserved, etc. |
| **N-4** | **Training & Enablement** | Training resources, certification paths, documentation, ongoing learning support. |
| **N-5** | **Professional Services** | Implementation support options and quality assurance for third-party implementers. |
| **N-6** | **Innovation Roadmap** | Upcoming features relevant to stated requirements (12-month horizon). |

